		        <li>1 vanilla bean</li>
	   			<li>2 cups half-and-half</li>
				<li>2 cups whipping cream, unwhipped</li>
				<li>1 (14 ounce) can EAGLE BRANDÂ® Sweetened Condensed Milk (NOT evaporated milk)</li>
		    </ul>
		
		    <ol>
		        <li>Split vanilla bean lengthwise; scrape out seeds or use vanilla extract. In large bowl, combine all ingredients; mix well.</li>
	   			<li>Pour into ice cream freezer container. Freeze according to manufacturers instructions. Freeze leftovers.</li>
